description:
Have you ever fantasized about the girl next door? What if the girl next door didn't turn out to be the sweet innocent girl you thought she was? What if she was a twisted, evil sadistic vixen that kept slaveboys in her basement just for her amusement? She loves to give pain, humiliate and use boys as her fuck toys.
Bobbi is the perfect girl next door but with a secret. Nobody knows about the dirty things she does to boys in the basement and unfortunately for Kade nobodys ever going to find out! Watch her flip her lid at the drop of a hat because Kade can't seem to do anything right! The girl next door never looked so good!
title: Psycho Bitch
